title: The best Locksmith services in the Fremont  Metro area
name: The best Locksmith services in the Fremont  Metro area

properties.name: Car Locksmith Alameda- Emergency Lockout & Lock Re-Key
properties.description: Posted by Ethelindaaubree 875 Island Dr Ste A 183, Alameda, CA, 94502My fiancé and I switched cars the other day, and I headed out to work after her, well it turned out I forgot to give her the garage door opener! So when she returned home she couldn’t get into the garage (or the house)! I thought that our engagement was going to end right then and there! I called to Car Locksmith Alameda- Emergency Lockout & Lock Re-Key at (510) 991-3616 and they sent someone over to the house right away to unlocked the door, and my fiancé had them make us an extra remote on the spot. Well done!

properties.name: Car Locksmith Antioch- Auto Lockout- Auto Lockout
properties.description: Posted by Ethelindaaubree 2974 Delta Fair Blvd # 278, Antioch, 94509, CACar Locksmith: We came home for a weekend up at the cottage and right away noticed something was wrong. Someone had tried to break into the house while we were away. Thankfully they weren’t successful however the managed to completely destroy the front door lock in the process. We called Available Locksmith at (925) 309-6247. They were able to send someone over right away to install a new lock, they even had one in stock that matched the front door! They were fast, efficient, and the price was reasonable!
